---
import Base from '../../layouts/Base.astro';
---
<Base title="英语学习中心" desc="生词本（SM-2 间隔重复）、听写拼写、真人发音，以及可选的 AI 词源讲解与口语陪练；数据全存本地">
<main class="wrap reader enx">
  <a class="back mono" href="/lang/">← 外语</a>
  <h1 class="rd-title">英语学习中心</h1>
  <div class="meta mono">
    <span class="sw" style="background:var(--c-ai);"></span>
    <span>间隔重复 · 真人发音 · 听写 · AI 词源讲解与陪练（可选）</span>
  </div>
  <p class="enx-sub">
    每天从「今日复习」开始，算法决定复习什么，你只管作答。生词、进度、AI Key 全部只存在你自己的浏览器里。
  </p>

  <div class="enx-app">
    <nav class="enx-side mono" aria-label="学习模块">
      <button type="button" class="on" data-p="rev"><i class="sw" style="background:var(--c-ai);"></i>今日复习<em id="nav-due"></em></button>
      <button type="button" data-p="book"><i class="sw" style="background:var(--c-base);"></i>生词本</button>
      <button type="button" data-p="dict"><i class="sw" style="background:var(--c-char);"></i>听写拼写</button>
      <button type="button" data-p="ai"><i class="sw" style="background:var(--c-tool);"></i>词典 · AI 讲解</button>
      <button type="button" data-p="chat"><i class="sw" style="background:var(--c-life);"></i>口语陪练</button>
      <button type="button" data-p="set"><i class="sw" style="background:var(--ink2);"></i>设置</button>
    </nav>

    <div class="enx-main">
      <!-- 今日复习 -->
      <section class="enx-panel" data-p="rev">
        <div class="enx-stats">
          <div class="enx-tile hot"><b id="st-due">0</b><span>待复习</span></div>
          <div class="enx-tile good"><b id="st-today">0</b><span>今日已复习</span></div>
          <div class="enx-tile"><b id="st-streak">0</b><span>连续天数</span></div>
          <div class="enx-tile"><b id="st-total">0</b><span>生词总量</span></div>
        </div>
        <div class="enx-prog"><i id="rev-prog"></i></div>
        <div id="rev-card" class="en-card"></div>
        <div class="en-hint mono">
          <kbd>空格</kbd> 显示释义　<kbd>1</kbd> 忘了　<kbd>2</kbd> 模糊　<kbd>3</kbd> 认识　<kbd>P</kbd> 发音
          　·　忘了的词 10 分钟内重现，认识的按 1 → 6 → 更长天数安排
        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- 生词本 -->
      <section class="enx-panel" data-p="book" hidden>
        <div class="enx-h">添加生词</div>
        <div class="enx-bar">
          <input id="book-w" type="text" class="mono" placeholder="单词，如 serendipity" style="width:180px;" />
          <input id="book-d" type="text" placeholder="释义（可点「查释义」自动填）" style="flex:1; min-width:200px; max-width:340px;" />
          <button type="button" class="pie-btn" id="book-fill">查释义</button>
          <button type="button" class="pie-btn primary" id="book-add">添加</button>
          <span class="mono enx-msg" id="book-msg"></span>
        </div>
        <div class="enx-h">词包</div>
        <div class="enx-packs" id="book-packs"></div>
        <div class="enx-h">全部生词</div>
        <div class="enx-bar slim">
          <input id="book-q" type="text" placeholder="搜索词或释义…" style="width:220px;" />
          <span class="mono enx-msg" id="book-count"></span>
        </div>
        <div id="book-list" class="en-book"></div>
      </section>

      <!-- 听写 -->
      <section class="enx-panel" data-p="dict" hidden>
        <div class="enx-h">听写拼写 —— 用耳朵替代眼睛</div>
        <div class="enx-bar">
          <label>范围
            <select id="dict-scope" class="mono">
              <option value="all">全部生词</option>
              <option value="due">待复习的</option>
            </select>
          </label>
          <button type="button" class="pie-btn primary" id="dict-start">▶ 开始 / 下一个</button>
          <button type="button" class="pie-btn" id="dict-replay">🔊 再听一遍</button>
        </div>
        <div class="en-card dictation">
          <div class="mono en-dictmsg" id="dict-msg">点「开始」出题</div>
          <div class="en-dictrow">
            <input id="dict-input" type="text" class="en-dictin mono" autocomplete="off" spellcheck="false" placeholder="听到什么拼什么，回车提交" />
            <button type="button" class="pie-btn primary" id="dict-check">提交</button>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- 词典 & AI -->
      <section class="enx-panel" data-p="ai" hidden>
        <div class="enx-h">查词 —— 词典免费即用，AI 讲词源（需配 Key）</div>
        <div class="enx-bar">
          <input id="ai-word" type="text" class="mono" placeholder="输入单词，回车查词典" style="width:200px;" />
          <button type="button" class="pie-btn primary" id="lk-go">查词典</button>
          <button type="button" class="pie-btn" id="ai-go">AI 讲解</button>
          <button type="button" class="pie-btn" id="ai-spk">🔊 发音</button>
        </div>
        <div id="lookup-out" class="en-lookup" hidden></div>
        <pre id="ai-out" class="en-aiout"></pre>
        <p class="mono enx-note">词典：dictionaryapi.dev / freedictionaryapi.com（公开源，含真人发音）· AI 讲解含词源词根拆解，结果本地缓存</p>
      </section>

      <!-- 口语陪练 -->
      <section class="enx-panel" data-p="chat" hidden>
        <div class="enx-h">口语陪练 Alex —— 多提问让你开口，纠错温和</div>
        <div class="enx-bar slim">
          <label class="mono"><input type="checkbox" id="chat-fix" checked /> 纠错模式</label>
          <button type="button" class="pie-btn" id="chat-clear">清空对话</button>
        </div>
        <div id="chat-log" class="en-chat"></div>
        <div class="en-dictrow" style="max-width:820px;">
          <input id="chat-input" type="text" class="en-dictin" autocomplete="off" placeholder="Say something in English… (回车发送)" />
          <button type="button" class="pie-btn primary" id="chat-send">发送</button>
        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- 设置 -->
      <section class="enx-panel" data-p="set" hidden>
        <div class="enx-h">发音</div>
        <div class="enx-bar">
          <label>音源
            <select id="en-aud" class="mono">
              <option value="auto">真人发音优先（推荐）</option>
              <option value="tts">仅浏览器 TTS</option>
            </select>
          </label>
          <label>口音
            <select id="en-acc" class="mono">
              <option value="us">美音</option>
              <option value="uk">英音</option>
            </select>
          </label>
          <label>TTS 音色 <select id="en-voice" class="mono" style="max-width:240px;"><option>（加载中…）</option></select></label>
          <label>语速 <input id="en-rate" type="range" min="0.6" max="1.3" step="0.05" style="width:110px;" /></label>
          <button type="button" class="pie-btn" id="en-try">试听 TTS</button>
        </div>
        <p class="mono enx-note">真人发音来自公开词典源的录音（美/英），首次播放需联网，之后走缓存；TTS 为完全离线的兜底。</p>

        <div class="enx-h">AI 服务（OpenAI 兼容 · BYOK）</div>
        <div class="enx-bar col">
          <label>预设
            <select id="set-preset" class="mono">
              <option value="">自定义</option>
              <option value="deepseek">DeepSeek</option>
              <option value="glm">智谱 GLM-4-Flash（免费）</option>
              <option value="kimi">Kimi (Moonshot)</option>
              <option value="openai">OpenAI</option>
            </select>
          </label>
          <label>接口地址 <input id="set-base" type="text" class="mono" style="width:320px;" /></label>
          <label>API Key <input id="set-key" type="password" class="mono" style="width:320px;" placeholder="sk-…" /></label>
          <label>模型 <input id="set-model" type="text" class="mono" style="width:200px;" /></label>
          <div style="display:flex; gap:10px; align-items:center;">
            <button type="button" class="pie-btn primary" id="set-save">保存</button>
            <button type="button" class="pie-btn" id="set-test">测试连接</button>
            <span class="mono enx-msg" id="set-msg"></span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <p class="mono enx-note">Key 只保存在你自己的浏览器 localStorage，请求从你的浏览器直连服务商 —— 本站没有服务器，也无法看到你的 Key。</p>

        <div class="enx-h">数据</div>
        <div class="enx-bar">
          <button type="button" class="pie-btn" id="set-export">导出生词本 (JSON)</button>
          <label class="pie-btn" style="cursor:pointer;">导入 JSON<input id="set-import" type="file" accept=".json" hidden /></label>
          <button type="button" class="pie-btn" id="set-wipe" style="color:var(--c-render);">清空全部数据</button>
        </div>
      </section>
    </div>
  </div>

  <p class="mono" style="max-width:1000px; color:var(--ink2); font-size:11.5px; margin-top:26px;">
    复习算法为 SM-2 简化版；未配置 AI 时其余功能完全可用。词典与发音数据来自公开源，学习数据不出你的浏览器。
  </p>
</main>
</Base>

<script>
  import '../../scripts/lang/english.js';
</script>
